A crumbling ancient stone bridge spanning a dark chasm, with missing and broken stones throughout its structure, yet still bearing the weight of a complex network of glowing fiber optic cables and data streams flowing across it. The bridge shows visible cracks and makeshift wooden repairs holding it together. Below in the shadows, more cables hang precariously. The scene is rendered in a cyberpunk style with neon blue and orange data streams contrasting against weathered gray stone and rusted metal patches. Rain falls through shafts of dim light from above, creating reflections on wet surfaces. The atmosphere conveys something functional but fragile, held together by temporary fixes, with the weight of modern demands pressing down on aging infrastructure.
